            <div id="_j_photo_181216268" data-seq="181216270" data-pid="181216268" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_6580859/181216268.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:365px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/C5/99/wKgBZ1h_FPiAagotAA2j8OR4fKs50.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/C5/99/wKgBZ1h_FPiAagotAA2j8OR4fKs50.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="181216268" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_181216267" data-seq="181216269" data-pid="181216267" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_6580859/181216267.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:362px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://a3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/C5/97/wKgBZ1h_FPaAC69aAAUG1yvgzsA07.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://a3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/C5/97/wKgBZ1h_FPaAC69aAAUG1yvgzsA07.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="181216267" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="181055028">
            不知从何时开始，雾霾成了这个季节的代名词，尤其是生活在北方的人更深有体会。十二月的北方就仿佛笼罩在一片夹杂着不知名气味的烟云当中。许多景色都失掉了原有的韵味。这次有幸接到“2016雪佛兰最美<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="中国" target="_blank">中国</a>行”的活动邀请，奔赴<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12938.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海南" target="_blank">海南</a>岛，与一群深受雾霾之扰的汽车媒体朋友们开启一段阳光灿烂的<a href="http://zuche.mafengwo.cn/jump_landing_page.php?keyword=%E8%87%AA%E9%A9%BE" class="link" data-kw="自驾"  target="_blank">自驾</a>之行。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_181059174" data-seq="181059175" data-pid="181059174" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_6580859/181059174.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/51/0F/wKgBZ1h92cyABDbbAA3zCaaqylk72.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/51/0F/wKgBZ1h92cyABDbbAA3zCaaqylk72.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="181059174" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div data-seq="181059349" data-index="3" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t1"><span class="_j_anchor">关于最美中国行</span></h2>
            </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="181059702">
            “勇闯新境”——最美<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="中国" target="_blank">中国</a>行是由汽车品牌雪佛兰组织发起的，自十一黄金周开始到年底，为期三个月，精心挑选十条横贯东西、纵穿南北的最美<a href="http://zuche.mafengwo.cn/jump_landing_page.php?keyword=%E8%87%AA%E9%A9%BE" class="link" data-kw="自驾"  target="_blank">自驾</a>路线，揽尽<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21536.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="中国" target="_blank">中国</a>大地上独具特色的如画风景。<br />
驰骋川藏公路、骑行最美<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/23934.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="江南" target="_blank">江南</a>、寻踪<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12976.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="山东" target="_blank">山东</a>古韵、探幽<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/44520.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="徽州" target="_blank">徽州</a>古迹、征服挂壁公路、寻访武夷人家、穿行大美<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/13287.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="湘西" target="_blank">湘西</a>、北上踏雪冰城、<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12938.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海南" target="_blank">海南</a>环岛之旅等，一路上，都有全新雪佛兰<a href="http://zuche.mafengwo.cn/jump_landing_page.php?keyword=SUV" class="link" data-kw="SUV"  target="_blank">SUV</a>创酷陪你前行。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_181061297" data-seq="181061298" data-pid="181061297" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_6580859/181061297.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/52/A9/wKgBZ1h93KyAH4foAAWI1PjlLM034.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/52/A9/wKgBZ1h93KyAH4foAAWI1PjlLM034.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="181061297" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="182259683">
            行驶在<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12938.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海南" target="_blank">海南</a>的<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11626.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="临海" target="_blank">临海</a>公路，红与蓝的交互辉映
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_181061139" data-seq="181061140" data-pid="181061139" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_6580859/181061139.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/52/85/wKgBZ1h93GOAW2Z8AAsezr1hzCI27.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/52/85/wKgBZ1h93GOAW2Z8AAsezr1hzCI27.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="181061139" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="182259522">
            潇洒地过弯，留下一阵尘烟随风飘逝。。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_182108775" data-seq="182257380" data-pid="182108775" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_6580859/182108775.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/43/81/wKgBZ1iFxNyAXDwwAAZJ49Q8NS428.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/43/81/wKgBZ1iFxNyAXDwwAAZJ49Q8NS428.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="182108775" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="182257798">
            雪佛兰新款创酷采用了黑色与棕色双拼的内饰配色，同时还配有金属质感的点缀，视觉效果更加年轻。中控台的7英寸显示屏搭载了新一代雪佛兰MyLink智能车载互联系统，该系统还带有百度Carlife功能。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_181253830" data-seq="182258182" data-pid="181253830" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_6580859/181253830.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/DF/3D/wKgBZ1h_PK-AJCAQAAhVypKwGUI67.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/DF/3D/wKgBZ1h_PK-AJCAQAAhVypKwGUI67.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="181253830" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="182258220">
            有内容还不够，外形吸引眼球才是硬道理。外观方面，新款创酷采用了雪佛兰最新家族式设计元素，精悍硬朗的前脸显得更加年轻、动感。同时，新车还配备了U型LED日间行车灯，来提高其辨识度，一路驶来，仿佛一只只小精灵在丛林中穿梭。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_182257527" data-seq="182257528" data-pid="182257527" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_6580859/182257527.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B8/65/wKgBZ1iG9YKAcAGWAAVY-xLIvt087.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B8/65/wKgBZ1iG9YKAcAGWAAVY-xLIvt087.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="182257527" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="182259788">
            这次我们一辆车3,4个人一起轮流开，所以也有幸驾驶创酷行驶了一段路程。（上图是同车大哥，我开的时候忘了拍张照。Orz.....）骨叔作为十几年驾龄的老司机，第一次随着车队驾驶体验也是十分新鲜。创酷这款6速手自一体变速箱完全是一副老好人的样子，换挡迅速、<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/63948.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="平顺" target="_blank">平顺</a>，很少有恼人的顿挫。它与发动机匹配很好，随着你的油门动作，动力循序渐进，不会出现深踩油门动力断档的情况。
        </p>
            <div data-seq="181062004" data-index="4" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t1"><span class="_j_anchor">关于行程</span></h2>
            </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="181061548">
            此次<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12938.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海南" target="_blank">海南</a>站的活动起点和终点都设在<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10513.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海口" target="_blank">海口</a>市。我们从<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10513.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海口" target="_blank">海口</a>出发，首先经过东郊椰林前往<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11616.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="万宁" target="_blank">万宁</a>入住。随后去往风景优美的亚龙湾热带天堂森林公园，之后抵达<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10030.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚" target="_blank">三亚</a>湾入住，最后经<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10781.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="儋州" target="_blank">儋州</a>休整，回到<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10513.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海口" target="_blank">海口</a>。全程4天，<a href="http://zuche.mafengwo.cn/jump_landing_page.php?keyword=%E8%87%AA%E9%A9%BE" class="link" data-kw="自驾"  target="_blank">自驾</a>行驶800多公里。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_181064022" data-seq="181064023" data-pid="181064022" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_6580859/181064022.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:542px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://a2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/55/0C/wKgBZ1h94FqAPb1hAAYbNr_nNfo27.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://a2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/55/0C/wKgBZ1h94FqAPb1hAAYbNr_nNfo27.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="181064022" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div data-seq="181070311" data-index="5" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t1"><span class="_j_anchor">东郊椰林</span></h2>
            </div>
            <div  class="add_video _j_seqitem " data-vid="177250" data-seq="181249944" data-url="889E96EEA0E574D09C33DC5901307461" data-type="0" data-ready="1">
    </div>
            <div  class="add_video _j_seqitem " data-vid="177247" data-seq="181248635" data-url="6B3F7D330BC4574E9C33DC5901307461" data-type="0" data-ready="1">
    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="181249353">
            到达<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10513.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海口" target="_blank">海口</a>的时候已经是半夜了，作为一个吃货的我，酒店没回，直奔夜宵去了。
        </p>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="181209783">
            此行我们整个车队有10部车，并有教练带头车非常有秩序的跑起来，每次先由最后一部车占道之后再一次变道，确保安全，每部车内大概3-4位，可以选择自由安排驾驶。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_181065522" data-seq="181065525" data-pid="181065522" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_6580859/181065522.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/56/18/wKgBZ1h94jqAQHceAAnaOoOH7qc70.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/56/18/wKgBZ1h94jqAQHceAAnaOoOH7qc70.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="181065522" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_181065524" data-seq="181065526" data-pid="181065524" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_6580859/181065524.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/56/1E/wKgBZ1h94kCAFEQGAAiOXqyJvkc88.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/56/1E/wKgBZ1h94kCAFEQGAAiOXqyJvkc88.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="181065524" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="181065392">
            第一段的路程比较舒适，平整路面行驶并没能给创酷更多的表现机会。沿着秀美的海岸线大道上，一辆辆红色的倩影穿梭在两侧层层椰林之间，描绘出一幅散发着动感、时尚和自然的优美画卷。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_179972460" data-seq="179972544" data-pid="179972460" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="5438385">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_6580859/179972460.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://a1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/DA/68/wKgBZ1h3MuqAdhDiABxhG8kPcF812.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://a1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/DA/68/wKgBZ1h3MuqAdhDiABxhG8kPcF812.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="179972460" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/5438385.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="5438385" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>东郊椰林风景名胜区
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="181068128">
            中午时分，车队抵达此行第一站——东郊椰林。<br />
海风轻拂，沙滩细腻，椰林摩挲，让人的心情瞬间放松下来。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_179972461" data-seq="179972545" data-pid="179972461" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="5438385">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_6580859/179972461.html">
